reviews_data.review_text: I was interested in buying a piece of banana bread if the lady hadn't been breathing all over it as she was talking to me...like why do yall not have a cover over the bread? Especially if it's sitting where you stand and talk. They don't have many options to just grab n go. you gotta place orders. The sweet life bakery up the street is better.

The lady was very sweet but I didn't love the product. The cookies tasted stale. And they don't have enough items available for purchase. Nothing eye catching either. You have to order a couple days ahead and I personally don't have the time when I'm looking to grab something quickly for my kids or coworkers. So I went somewhere else. That's just my experience.

reviews_data.review_text: Delicious!
Awesome!!!! The cookies were delicious and the lemon bars were out of this world!!! I would highly recommend!!!! You will not be disappointed!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much! Hope to see you again soon.

reviews_data.review_text: Everything is so fresh and delicious!!! You have got to try it.

Wow what a gem. I did not know this place existed until I happened to drive down Wilshire. I had to try the cheese cake which looked delicious and was. Many cheesecakes are dense lumps of sweetened cream cheese but this had the perfect balance of cheese and cake. I also got a loaf of bread which was fresh. Light and fluffy and tasted delicious.
I liked the cheese cake so much I returned the next day for another slice. I met the owner/Baker and she is very friendly. I also left with 2 macaroons with a dark chocolate enhancement. These are fantastic. I plant to become a regular customer. Try p3:6. You will not be disappointed.
Stopped by on a whim the other day and everything is amazing! One of the best slices of cheesecake I've ever had. We also got cookies, cupcakes and its all great. I will definitely stop by again!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much! We are so glad you liked everything. Hope to see you soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Stopped in this morning for the first time and got a yummy cinnamon roll. SO good. They had a great variety of freshly baked goodies...cookies, cakes, pies and breads. I will definitely visit again soon.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much!

reviews_data.review_text: Best service! Loved the brownies and have special orders awesome new spot!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text:
So we have gone here twice now, back to back weekends. They have pastries, cookies, eclairs, it varies. This is a locally owned business. Their bread is amazing, just make sure you leave a loaf for us to buy on a Sat. ;)

Seriously try the bread. I'm hoping to try other bread flavors but with their hours can only swing by on a Sat. So, we got one yesterday fresh out of the oven! Amazing...came home cut, add butter. Yum. Anyways their cookies and other items are great too. Give them a try!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much. We are glad you enjoyed it and hope to be adding more breads to the menu soon.

reviews_data.review_text:
I love pastries and always trying to support local.

Chocolate cookies are a must and salted brownie was awesome!!
Will return

reviews_data.review_text: Amazing!!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you! Hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Absolutely delicious, my whole family is hooked. I highly recommend the salted caramel brownie or smore's brownie. We recently discovered the homemade bread and OMG. So delicious.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much! We look forward to serving you again soon!
